@progers1618:

What tracker entries, if any, that you include in a torrent file that you upload to TPB, is not really relevant, since every torrent file is automatically edited by the system to include trackers of our choice.
Thank you so much for this!!! This show has changed my life over the years, and yes, I did just donate! :) Long live Ira Glass and the gang! Cheers!
